title: Independiente de Neuquén
text:
Club Atlético Independiente (more often referred as Independiente de Neuquén) is an <a href="Argentina">Argentine</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> club based in the city of <a href="Neuqu%C3%A9n">Neuquén</a>. The squad currently plays in Zone A of the regionalised 3rd level of Argentine football <a href="Torneo%20Federal%20A">Torneo Federal A</a>.
"El Albirrojo" is the only club from the <a href="Neuqu%C3%A9n%20Province">Neuquén Province</a> which plays in the Argentine third division league.
